positioning

1. static
		- all elements are assigneed by default .
		- elements show up top botom, left to right in the flow of the document
2. absolute
		-positions the element at x, y coordinates
		-takes the document out of the flow of the document
3. relative
		- positions the element relative to where it would show up in the flow of the document
4. fixed
		- positions the element at the x, y coordinate
			-relative to the browser window
		- take element out of the flow of doc